#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:4
msgid "CLI Reference"
msgstr "CLI tilvísun"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:7
msgid "Synopsis"
msgstr "Yfirlit"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:14
msgid "If no files are given, ``snapper`` reads from stdin and writes to stdout."
msgstr "Ef engar skrár eru gefnar les ``snapper`` af stdin og skrifar á stdout."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:17
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Valkostir"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:20
msgid "``-f``, ``--format <FORMAT>``"
msgstr "``-f``, ``--format <FORMAT>``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:22
msgid "Input format. One of: ``org``, ``latex``, ``markdown``, ``plaintext``."
msgstr "Inntakssnið. Eitt af: ``org``, ``latex``, ``markdown``, ``plaintext``."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:25
msgid ""
"Auto-detected from file extension when omitted. Defaults to ``plaintext``"
" for stdin."
msgstr ""
"Sjálfgreinist frá skráarendingu þegar sleppt er. Sjálfgefið er "
"``plaintext`` fyrir stdin."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:29
msgid "``--stdin-filepath <PATH>``"
msgstr "``--stdin-filepath <PATH>``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:31
msgid ""
"Assume this filename when reading stdin, for format auto-detection. "
"Useful for editor integrations that pipe buffer contents."
msgstr ""
"Gera ráð fyrir þessu skráarheiti þegar lesið er af stdin, fyrir "
"sjálfvirka sniðgreiningu. Gagnlegt fyrir samþættingu ritla sem pípa "
"innihald biðminnis."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:34
msgid "Example: ``cat paper.org | snapper --stdin-filepath paper.org``"
msgstr "Dæmi: ``cat paper.org | snapper --stdin-filepath paper.org``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:37
msgid "``-o``, ``--output <FILE>``"
msgstr "``-o``, ``--output <FILE>``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:39
msgid "Write output to a file instead of stdout."
msgstr "Skrifa úttak í skrá í stað stdout."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:42
msgid "``-i``, ``--in-place``"
msgstr "``-i``, ``--in-place``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:44
msgid "Modify input files in place. Requires file arguments (not stdin)."
msgstr "Breyta inntaksskrám á staðnum. Krefst skráarviðfanga (ekki stdin)."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:48
msgid "``-w``, ``--max-width <N>``"
msgstr "``-w``, ``--max-width <N>``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:50
msgid ""
"Maximum line width. Sentences exceeding this width are wrapped at word "
"boundaries using ``textwrap``. Default: ``0`` (unlimited). Also respects "
"``max_line_length`` from ``.editorconfig`` if present."
msgstr ""
"Hámarkslínubreidd. Setningar sem fara yfir þessa breidd eru umbrotnar við "
"orðamörk með ``textwrap``. Sjálfgefið: ``0`` (ótakmarkað). Virðir einnig "
"``max_line_length`` úr ``.editorconfig`` ef til staðar."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:56
msgid "``--check``"
msgstr "``--check``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:58
msgid ""
"Check mode for CI. Exits with code 1 if any file would change, without "
"modifying anything. Prints the paths of files that would be reformatted "
"to stderr."
msgstr ""
"Prófunarstilling fyrir CI. Hættir með kóða 1 ef einhver skrá myndi "
"breytast, án þess að breyta neinu. Prentar slóðir skráa sem myndu "
"endursníðast á stderr."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:63
msgid "``--diff``"
msgstr "``--diff``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:65
msgid ""
"Show a unified diff of what would change, without modifying anything. "
"Useful for reviewing before committing. Exits with code 1 if any file "
"would change."
msgstr ""
"Sýna sameinaðan diff af því sem myndi breytast, án þess að breyta neinu. "
"Gagnlegt til rýni áður en lagt er inn. Hættir með kóða 1 ef einhver skrá "
"myndi breytast."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:70
msgid "``--range <START:END>``"
msgstr "``--range <START:END>``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:72
msgid ""
"Only format lines in the given range (1-indexed, inclusive). Lines "
"outside the range pass through unchanged. Useful for editor format-"
"selection integrations."
msgstr ""
"Aðeins sníða línur innan tiltekins bils (1-númerað, meðtalið). Línur "
"utan bilsins fara í gegn óbreyttar. Gagnlegt fyrir samþættingu "
"sniðvals í ritli."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:76
msgid "Example: ``snapper --range 10:20 paper.org``"
msgstr "Dæmi: ``snapper --range 10:20 paper.org``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:79
msgid "``--output-format <text|json|sarif>``"
msgstr "``--output-format <text|json|sarif>``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:81
msgid ""
"Output format for ``--check`` mode. Default: ``text`` (prints filenames "
"to stderr)."
msgstr ""
"Úttakssnið fyrir ``--check`` stillingu. Sjálfgefið: ``text`` (prentar "
"skráarnöfn á stderr)."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:84
msgid "``json`` : outputs a JSON array with file paths and line counts"
msgstr "``json`` : skilar JSON-fylki með skráarslóðum og línufjölda"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:86
msgid "``sarif`` : outputs SARIF v2.1.0 for GitHub Code Scanning integration"
msgstr "``sarif`` : skilar SARIF v2.1.0 fyrir GitHub Code Scanning samþættingu"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:89
msgid "``--neural``"
msgstr "``--neural``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:91
msgid ""
"Use neural sentence detection via nnsplit (byte-level LSTM, tract "
"backend). Downloads and caches the model (~4MB) to ``~/.cache/nnsplit/`` "
"on first use. Rule-based detection remains the default (faster, better "
"abbreviation handling). Neural excels for non-English text."
msgstr ""
"Nota taugakerfisstuðða setningargreiningu gegnum nnsplit (bæta-stigs "
"LSTM, tract-bakendi). Hleður niður og vistar eredlíkanið (~4MB) í "
"``~/.cache/nnsplit/`` við fyrstu notkun. Reglubundin greining er "
"áfram sjálfgefin (hraðvirkari, betri meðhöndlun skammstafana). "
"Taugakerfisgreining er yfirburða fyrir texta á öðrum tungumálum en ensku."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:97
msgid "``--lang <CODE>``"
msgstr "``--lang <CODE>``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:99
msgid ""
"Language for neural sentence detection. Default: ``en``. Available: "
"``en``, ``de``, ``fr``, ``no``, ``sv``, ``zh``, ``tr``, ``ru``, ``uk``."
msgstr ""
"Tungumál fyrir taugakerfissetningargreiningu. Sjálfgefið: ``en``. "
"Tiltæk: ``en``, ``de``, ``fr``, ``no``, ``sv``, ``zh``, ``tr``, "
"``ru``, ``uk``."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:104
msgid "``--model-path <PATH>``"
msgstr "``--model-path <PATH>``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:106
msgid ""
"Path to a custom ONNX model file for neural detection. Overrides "
"``--lang``."
msgstr ""
"Slóð að sérsniðinni ONNX eredlíkansskrá fyrir taugakerfisgreiningu. "
"Yfirgegnir ``--lang``."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:110
msgid "``--config <PATH>``"
msgstr "``--config <PATH>``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:112
msgid ""
"Path to a ``.snapperrc.toml`` config file. When omitted, ``snapper`` "
"searches from the current directory upward."
msgstr ""
"Slóð að ``.snapperrc.toml`` stillingarskrá. Þegar sleppt er leitar "
"``snapper`` frá núverandi möppu og upp á við."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:116
msgid "``-h``, ``--help``"
msgstr "``-h``, ``--help``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:118
msgid "Print help message."
msgstr "Prenta hjálparskilaboð."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:121
msgid "``-V``, ``--version``"
msgstr "``-V``, ``--version``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:123
msgid "Print version."
msgstr "Prenta útgáfunúmer."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:126
msgid "Subcommands"
msgstr "Undirskipanir"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:129
msgid "``snapper init``"
msgstr "``snapper init``"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:131
msgid ""
"Initialize snapper for a project. Detects which prose formats exist in "
"the directory tree and generates:"
msgstr ""
"Frumstilla snapper fyrir verkefni. Greinir hvaða textasnið eru til "
"staðar í möpputrénu og býr til:"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:134
msgid "``.snapperrc.toml`` with sensible defaults"
msgstr "``.snapperrc.toml`` með skynsamlegum sjálfgildum"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:136
msgid "``.gitattributes`` entries for the git smudge/clean filter"
msgstr "``.gitattributes`` færslur fyrir git smudge/clean síuna"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:138
msgid "pre-commit hook snippet"
msgstr "pre-commit hook bútur"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:140
msgid "Apheleia (Emacs) configuration snippet"
msgstr "Apheleia (Emacs) stillingabútur"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:142
msgid "Use ``--dry-run`` to preview without writing files."
msgstr "Notaðu ``--dry-run`` til að forskoða án þess að skrifa skrár."

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:145
msgid "Exit codes"
msgstr "Útgangskóðar"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:147
msgid "``0`` : Success (or ``--check`` / ``--diff`` with no changes needed)"
msgstr "``0`` : Tókst (eða ``--check`` / ``--diff`` án breytinga)"

#: ../../source/reference/cli.rst:149
msgid ""
"``1`` : ``--check`` or ``--diff`` found files that would change, or any "
"error"
msgstr ""
"``1`` : ``--check`` eða ``--diff`` fann skrár sem myndu breytast, eða "
"einhver villa"

